thread.title: EXCLUSIVE: Walmart’s Uber, Lyft partnerships end

title: EXCLUSIVE: Walmart’s Uber, Lyft partnerships end
text:
Exclusive: Walmart’s Uber, Lyft partnerships end 47
If the idea of Uber and Lyft delivering groceries while shuttling around passengers sounded far fetched, it's now clear it was much harder plan to make reality than expected. Walmart's partnership with both companies is now over, according to an exclusive Reuters report.
